{"tid":132454,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好依賴自己男朋友","createTime":"2017-02-24T00:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T08:08:05.000Z","uid":33076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"429d37770d0e802f80619f95877f002af03d7537","tid":132454,"uid":33076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:31:28.000Z","msg":"日日習慣有佢<br />\n但佢一發脾氣就會唔理我講好難聽既說話<br />\n有時仲會block whatspp<br />\n一搵唔到佢就成個人失曬魂咁<br />\n嗰種感覺真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c346f45896c45e78797cfcb43b917b68b41f8b","tid":132454,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:36:51.000Z","msg":"唔好咁依賴一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56ca96f277cb71bee2a83f7357861b5a92d40b5","tid":132454,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:38:26.000Z","msg":"嘩 你條仔會打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分手啦痴根"},{"pid":"7cacf3df913209dfeb0d69baa9c5c78accfea11d","tid":132454,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩 你條仔會打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分手啦痴根</blockquote><br />\n點睇得出佢條仔打佢"},{"pid":"5ff0787734c482179f2cb9cca629783520f6c368","tid":132454,"uid":86394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:50:03.000Z","msg":"太依賴會被控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd1293c010cb9a56b2a26ac026bff862a841e09","tid":132454,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:50:15.000Z","msg":"搵多D野分散注意力"},{"pid":"d9ea13b9cd7877c988d17b1d567c33b60a623f6c","tid":132454,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:10:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc1665984a5624ec11841936709d63cbeee4febf","tid":132454,"uid":78540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:14:55.000Z","msg":"依賴佢雖然開心好有安全感但到最後只會令自己痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9770dd9c027e19e68b797c098e4eec505391600","tid":132454,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘩 你條仔會打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分手啦痴根</blockquote><br />\n點睇得出佢條仔打佢</blockquote><br />\n佢之前啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32524dfc4ce8da505f3c24d9816c03f55b25e206","tid":132454,"uid":87238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"不要這樣，我相信你以家都好辛苦，太依賴不是一件好的事情，到時又打你，你會點？"},{"pid":"aafe817b2f67bed7493211ce83b7ef57e01eae7b","tid":132454,"uid":80675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5faa0bd4e05b7cb42e60eb30150929599b261a07","tid":132454,"uid":45732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"唉 男人靠吾住架 自愛啦絲打"},{"pid":"c8594e6112d9f60ff1dc2a4d31f4dc00df04b743","tid":132454,"uid":43455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:56:18.000Z","msg":"冇 冇男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65fba4960a0107369ad452ba680818e84bdfb66","tid":132454,"uid":39720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T20:33:24.000Z","msg":"我 有咩大事小事都會搵佢 <br />\n佢對我都好有耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb36762c4b9a9e4ab87cce60de3f9c32fbf851d0","tid":132454,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T22:02:13.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n不過啱啱分左手 特別心痛<br />\n冇左精神支持"},{"pid":"c348623cf1f3527c0b42ea1d2e2a65a72ded7826","tid":132454,"uid":9792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:31:43.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過去二十年一直處於唔開心狀態<br />\n每日都有尋死嘅唸頭<br />\n直到識到現任我先知乜係開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能因為咁我好依賴佢<br />\n如果冇咗佢我諗我冇動力留係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好驚冇咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2018f7933fa9e40058567be85f267a45c6fde782","tid":132454,"uid":18863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"我覺得我太依賴男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直頭當咗佢係我生活既重心<br />\n好多野都會諗咗佢先 好多野佢都係優先<br />\n會為佢食唔安訓唔落<br />\n無時無刻都想知佢係邊 做緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但原來咁樣會對佢造成好大負擔<br />\n我都唔鐘意人地成為我生活既重心<br />\n唉 想分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：啱啱同居咗幾個月"},{"pid":"8f9fca179b7c3d4f8ca320e6f07a089519c21567","tid":132454,"uid":68258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"唔可以太依賴一個人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你緊張佢多過佢緊張你<br />\n等於你愛佢更多 多過愛自己<br />\n會冇咗自己 因為對方一啲野就唔開心<br />\n個種感覺難受到落左地獄<br />\n一個唔好彩分咗手 咁你就玩完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過愛一個人又點做到唔依賴啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a658940636e14f37c225d65293ac84de72cea4d","tid":132454,"uid":6334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過去二十年一直處於唔開心狀態<br />\n每日都有尋死嘅唸頭<br />\n直到識到現任我先知乜係開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能因為咁我好依賴佢<br />\n如果冇咗佢我諗我冇動力留係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好驚冇咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我ex大概同你一樣<br />\n但最後佢都係自殺左"},{"pid":"0bb6488a676bd593291d7c65ef287dbda2c4f846","tid":132454,"uid":9792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過去二十年一直處於唔開心狀態<br />\n每日都有尋死嘅唸頭<br />\n直到識到現任我先知乜係開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能因為咁我好依賴佢<br />\n如果冇咗佢我諗我冇動力留係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好驚冇咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我ex大概同你一樣<br />\n但最後佢都係自殺左</blockquote><br />\n希望可以以後同男朋友開開心心咁我就可以繼續有動力生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全明你個ex感受<br />\n我好彩嘅係我男朋友仲同我一齊<br />\n但我好驚有日會失去佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我諗我下場就會同你個ex一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acd1eb0c5a010e59b7e311d20dbeabcd2f452b4","tid":132454,"uid":47426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"我都好依賴我男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩依加番學番工，可以冇咁痴身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876c60cd349ff2b140bea2552b7ae1eb891ba200","tid":132454,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得我太依賴男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直頭當咗佢係我生活既重心<br />\n好多野都會諗咗佢先 好多野佢都係優先<br />\n會為佢食唔安訓唔落<br />\n無時無刻都想知佢係邊 做緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但原來咁樣會對佢造成好大負擔<br />\n我都唔鐘意人地成為我生活既重心<br />\n唉 想分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：啱啱同居咗幾個月</blockquote><br />\n我同你一樣<br />\n結果佢太攰了 分左手<br />\n要改啊 唔係個個受得住"}]}